`).join('')}

**AI Recommendations:**

ğŸ¯ **Immediate Actions:**
${data.services.filter(s => s.status === 'degraded').length > 0 
  ? `1. Address degraded services: ${data.services.filter(s => s.status === 'degraded').map(s => s.name).join(', ')}
2. Review service logs for error patterns`
